mindmap
  root((From Prototype to Product))
    Prototype Failure Modes
      Infrastructure absence
      Ownership vacuum
      Value misalignment
      Scaling collapse
    Shift Left Design
      Production parity tooling
      Versioning and reproducibility
      Progressive rollout
      Rollback and circuit breakers
    Product Thinking
      User-centered design
      Operational success metrics
      Feedback loops as design inputs
      UX, compliance, ops integration
    Cross-Functional Handoffs
      Ready model definition
      SLOs and interface contracts
      Documentation as system artifact
      Observability before handoff
    Readiness Assessment
      Latency and throughput targets
      Input validation and graceful failure
      Artifact versioning
      Drift detection and bias monitoring
      Failure scenario mapping
    Post-Deployment Lifecycle
      Feedback loop collection
      Controlled retraining pipelines
      Business KPI monitoring
      Model ownership and support
    CAIO as Orchestrator
      Cross-functional alignment
      Platform investment advocacy
      Lifecycle planning
      Experimentation within guardrails